      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.309</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1151e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="id2039C700EL4" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        Insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1057235.dita#i1057235"
                              base="i1057235"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.219-1</xref>, Small Business Program Representations, in solicitations exceeding the micro-purchase threshold when the contract will be performed in the United States or its outlying areas.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="id2039C7006LA" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        Use the provision with its Alternate I in solicitations issued by DoD, NASA, or the Coast Guard.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="id2039C80N0MW" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>Use the provision with its Alternate II in solicitations that will result in a multiple-award contract with more than one NAICS code assigned. This is authorized for solicitations issued after October 1, 2022 (see <xref href="FAR-i1101844.dita#i1101844"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">19.102</xref>(b)).<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 19.309 by adding paragraph (a)(3) and?></ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1172e50" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  When contracting by sealed bidding, insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1057302.dita#i1057302"
                        base="i1057302"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-2</xref>, Equal Low Bids, in solicitations when the contract will be performed in the United States or its outlyingareas.</p>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1172e62" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="id2039CA090IU" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>Insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1057874.dita#i1057874"
                                 base="i1057874"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">52.219-28</xref>, Post-Award Small Business Program Rerepresentation, in solicitations and contracts exceeding the micro-purchase threshold when the contract will be performed in the United States or its outlying areas.<?FM MARKER [Why] revising paragraph (c).?></ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="id2039CA0J0LK" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph ">Use the clause with its Alternate I in solicitations and the resulting multiple-award contracts with more than one NAICS code. This is authorized for solicitations issued after October 1, 2022 (see <xref href="FAR-i1101844.dita#i1101844"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">19.102</xref>(b)).</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
